_sText:
A fairly difficult Kz Bhop MAP!

HAve fun, if you want to port it to csgo i'll make your life easier with the original VMF add me on discord from the sourcejump discord

A fixed version, changes:

Boosters are now multi hop instead of 1hop to make it less rng on scroll.

Adjusted several parts.

Added several check points on the more unforgiving parts.

Moved last level ladder 6 units closer to make it more forgiving on scroll.

Cart is still on the map without textures. It's intended. Really.


PS! If you are having troubles with people downloading the wrong map from the server eventho you have deleted and cleared the old map from the server then it is most likely stored in the fast dl cache which you have to clear, if you don't have access to clear it then contact the people that run the fast dl and have them purge the file as it can take a while for it to disappear automatically.
